WEBVTT

00:13.990 --> 00:16.170
[The Night Before
the Staged Execution Rescue]

00:43.600 --> 00:48.770
♪ What's the cost
of going against the wind? ♪

00:49.600 --> 00:53.280
♪ Knowing you, knowing me,
we live up to our promises ♪

00:53.300 --> 00:57.500
♪ Aligning the traces of our conviction ♪

00:57.620 --> 01:00.090
♪ As long as I'm with you ♪

01:00.110 --> 01:03.090
♪ The journey can stretch on forever ♪

01:03.120 --> 01:06.870
♪ Even if it puts my life on the line ♪

01:06.310 --> 01:07.640
Tomorrow's fake rescue
from the execution ground

01:06.890 --> 01:09.590
♪ I shall never forget ♪

01:08.110 --> 01:09.640
is a life-or-death gamble.

01:09.789 --> 01:11.430
If this charade isn't convincing enough,

01:11.430 --> 01:13.630
we won't gain the trust of Northern Qin.

01:13.680 --> 01:15.710
You must strike me down without mercy,

01:15.710 --> 01:17.310
and I won't hold back either.

01:18.060 --> 01:20.120
I'll try my best to keep you all alive.

01:20.150 --> 01:21.560
But swords and blades have no eyes—

01:21.560 --> 01:23.120
there's always a chance of an accident.

01:23.120 --> 01:24.840
-If anything were to...
-Your Highness, no need to say more.

01:24.840 --> 01:26.920
Death is inevitable on the battlefield.

01:26.920 --> 01:28.150
If this plan succeeds, it can at least

01:28.150 --> 01:30.350
secure more than a decade of peace
and stability for the Northern Border.

01:30.350 --> 01:32.039
We're willing to be the blade
in Your Highness's hand!

01:32.039 --> 01:36.789
-We're willing!
-To stand together through life and death!

01:37.070 --> 01:38.560
Your Highness, you once said,

01:38.560 --> 01:39.870
"Who says we stand alone?

01:39.870 --> 01:41.130
We share weal and woe."

01:42.020 --> 01:42.660
Alright!

01:43.600 --> 01:47.000
How fitting—"Who says we stand alone?
We share weal and woe."

01:47.300 --> 01:49.750
Then let's face life and death together!

03:17.740 --> 03:22.150
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

03:22.210 --> 03:25.060
[Episode 26]

03:25.140 --> 03:28.620
[Huiyin Hall]

03:36.190 --> 03:37.050
Say something.

03:38.400 --> 03:39.730
Come on, say something.

03:41.590 --> 03:43.910
Xie Jiayu! Our wedding's tomorrow.

03:44.240 --> 03:45.400
You have to marry me

03:45.910 --> 03:47.770
whether you're willing to or not!

03:54.240 --> 03:55.730
Keep breaking things like this,

03:55.730 --> 03:58.390
and there won't be many vases
left in the palace.

03:59.050 --> 04:01.280
How is it? Has His Majesty
issued the decree?

04:01.280 --> 04:03.210
Xiao Wuyi's judgment was correct.

04:03.310 --> 04:05.310
After the An and Lu families
were cleared of their charges,

04:05.310 --> 04:07.910
the people's anger over the false charges
fabricated by Northern Qin,

04:07.910 --> 04:10.280
along with their hatred stemming from
more than 2 decades of war,

04:10.280 --> 04:11.540
have reached its peak.

04:12.360 --> 04:14.950
Public support for the Northern Expedition
is now solid.

04:14.950 --> 04:16.959
His Majesty has issued a decree
approving the expedition

04:16.959 --> 04:19.190
and ordered He Yuan to draft
a proclamation for it.

04:19.190 --> 04:22.280
As expected, nothing escapes
his calculations.

04:25.560 --> 04:26.160
Li Mao!

04:26.320 --> 04:28.320
I'd rather die today than marry you!

04:35.720 --> 04:36.510
What's this?

04:36.690 --> 04:38.250
Don't you want to root out

04:38.450 --> 04:41.510
all the Northern Qin spies in the palace
before the Northern Expedition?

04:41.510 --> 04:43.360
This item is called the caltrop fireball.

04:43.360 --> 04:45.159
It is recorded in the surviving fragments
of "Essentials of Fire Attacks."

04:45.159 --> 04:46.950
Back then, Northern Qin was so desperate
to kill Cui Jun

04:46.950 --> 04:48.560
precisely because they wanted
to seize this item.

04:48.560 --> 04:50.680
Before my master, Yuan Xiaoliu,
passed away,

04:50.680 --> 04:52.360
he entrusted this blueprint to me.

04:52.360 --> 04:55.000
He said that the art of firearms

04:55.170 --> 04:57.030
was tied to the fate of the nation.

04:57.320 --> 04:59.330
So if the Northern Qin spies
learn of this item,

04:59.330 --> 05:00.390
even if it's a trap,

05:00.920 --> 05:03.450
they'll surely risk their lives
to obtain it.

05:04.480 --> 05:05.810
That's wonderful news.

05:05.960 --> 05:08.390
With this item, the Northern Expedition
is bound to succeed.

05:08.390 --> 05:10.000
But I've modified this blueprint.
So don't let

05:10.000 --> 05:12.040
the Directorate of Military Equipment
blindly manufacture them.

05:12.040 --> 05:13.400
If they end up
blowing themselves up instead,

05:13.400 --> 05:14.950
I won't take responsibility.

05:14.950 --> 05:15.680
Yaoyao.

05:19.720 --> 05:21.120
You still don't trust me.

05:23.540 --> 05:24.390
I trust you,

05:25.240 --> 05:27.240
but I also have to guard against you.

05:27.750 --> 05:29.420
Xiao Wuyi prides himself
on his cleverness—

05:29.420 --> 05:31.220
he factors in the people's will,

05:31.240 --> 05:32.770
and your ambitions as well.

05:33.020 --> 05:34.620
He thinks he's thought of everything,

05:34.620 --> 05:36.350
but in reality, he's just a fool

05:37.270 --> 05:39.000
who doesn't value his own life.

05:39.390 --> 05:41.360
That's why I'm his last line of defense.

05:41.360 --> 05:42.760
I can't take that chance.

05:43.080 --> 05:43.790
Mao.

05:44.680 --> 05:45.610
I won't harm you,

05:46.050 --> 05:47.980
but I won't let you harm him either.

05:48.090 --> 05:49.320
I just want both of you

05:50.409 --> 05:51.670
to stay alive and well.

05:58.190 --> 05:58.750
Alright.

05:59.750 --> 06:01.150
Then tomorrow's wedding

06:01.560 --> 06:04.220
will be the best opportunity
to catch the spies.

06:08.390 --> 06:10.020
Xie Jiayu, I'll give you one last chance!

06:10.020 --> 06:10.750
The wedding's tomorrow.

06:10.750 --> 06:11.830
Are you going to marry me or not?

06:11.830 --> 06:14.190
Will you give me the blueprints
for the caltrop fireball or not?

06:14.190 --> 06:16.780
If you're determined to die
alongside Xiao Wuyi,

06:16.780 --> 06:18.540
I'll kill Xiao Ziqi right now.

06:19.270 --> 06:19.720
You wouldn't dare!

06:19.720 --> 06:20.270
Feng An!

06:20.620 --> 06:21.400
Yes, Your Highness.

06:21.400 --> 06:23.600
Take Xiao Ziqi to
the Court of Judicial Review.

06:23.600 --> 06:24.700
Since his surname is Xiao,

06:24.700 --> 06:27.630
let him be reunited with his family
as soon as possible.

06:27.630 --> 06:28.360
Understood.

06:28.580 --> 06:29.570
Li Mao, you're out of your mind!

06:29.570 --> 06:31.170
You won't even spare a child?

06:32.600 --> 06:34.510
I've only kept him alive to make you obey,

06:34.510 --> 06:36.120
but my patience is running out.

06:36.120 --> 06:37.260
The Grand Tutor is dead,

06:37.260 --> 06:38.680
and the Xiao family has fallen.

06:38.680 --> 06:40.159
Now, aside from
my lingering affection for you,

06:40.159 --> 06:41.690
you have nothing to rely on.

06:42.159 --> 06:43.960
Stop overestimating yourself.

06:46.060 --> 06:48.390
You're nothing more than
my spoils of war.

06:49.720 --> 06:51.720
I'll give you the blueprints
for the caltrop fireball.

06:51.720 --> 06:54.050
But you must let Xiao Ziqi
and He Yuanji go.

06:54.230 --> 06:54.960
Fine.

06:54.990 --> 06:56.720
Let them go before the wedding!

06:57.360 --> 06:58.090
Okay.

07:20.750 --> 07:22.010
After all these years,

07:22.910 --> 07:24.640
you're still nothing like her.

07:27.120 --> 07:28.650
Forgive me, Your Highness.

07:31.320 --> 07:32.000
Never mind.

07:32.870 --> 07:34.270
Now that she's returned,

07:34.870 --> 07:37.130
you don't have to keep up the act anymore.

07:37.190 --> 07:39.520
Your Highness, please don't send me away.

07:39.870 --> 07:42.270
Please have pity on my devotion,
Your Highness.

07:42.270 --> 07:43.720
I'm willing to serve Your Highness

07:43.720 --> 07:45.470
and Her Highness the Secondary Consort.

07:45.470 --> 07:47.000
I've treated you so poorly,

07:47.640 --> 07:50.370
yet why have you still not
changed your feelings?

07:51.000 --> 07:53.330
I've served Your Highness all these years

07:53.720 --> 07:55.600
and know full well the hardships
Your Highness has faced.

07:55.600 --> 07:57.530
Even if I cannot be the one you love,

07:58.680 --> 08:01.480
I'm willing to be a bowl of tea or a lamp.

08:02.310 --> 08:03.480
As long as I can bring you

08:03.480 --> 08:05.140
a moment of peace and comfort,

08:06.430 --> 08:07.800
I'll feel content.

08:11.750 --> 08:12.560
Good.

08:13.310 --> 08:16.230
Then tomorrow, do something for me.

08:17.310 --> 08:18.630
Whatever Your Highness commands.

08:18.630 --> 08:19.960
Keep an eye on Xie Jiayu.

08:20.480 --> 08:22.750
If she tries to pass anything
to He Yuanji

08:22.750 --> 08:24.750
or Xiao Ziqi to take out of the palace,

08:24.750 --> 08:25.750
swap it out for me.

08:26.390 --> 08:29.720
That could be the key to victory
in the Northern Expedition.

08:30.820 --> 08:31.550
Understood.

08:31.970 --> 08:32.659
Also,

08:36.159 --> 08:37.440
avoid Feng An.

08:37.710 --> 08:39.240
He's a spy for Northern Qin.

08:40.789 --> 08:41.549
What?

08:42.960 --> 08:43.960
Eunuch Feng is...

08:51.360 --> 08:52.160
Chan.

08:53.790 --> 08:55.520
You're the only one I can trust.

08:57.270 --> 09:00.070
I'll do my utmost
to share Your Highness's burden.

09:28.790 --> 09:31.520
Your Highness, it's time to
return to the palace.

09:59.970 --> 10:00.690
Freeze!

10:05.630 --> 10:06.440
Hold on.

10:10.030 --> 10:11.270
Miss Chan,

10:11.360 --> 10:13.820
I entrust Young Lady to your care
from now on.

10:15.440 --> 10:16.070
Ziqi,

10:16.360 --> 10:18.030
hurry and thank Sister Chan.

10:19.680 --> 10:21.480
No need for such formalities,
Young Master.

10:21.480 --> 10:22.360
In the days to come,

10:22.360 --> 10:25.560
I'll definitely take good care of
your concubine mother.

10:35.670 --> 10:36.320
Let's go.

10:51.320 --> 10:52.920
Feng An has been discovered.

10:53.040 --> 10:56.000
The 3 people in his network
are likely all exposed now.

10:56.000 --> 10:56.600
Now,

10:56.840 --> 10:59.210
you're the only ones who can
get this blueprint out of the palace.

10:59.210 --> 11:00.330
Deliver this to His Highness immediately,

11:00.330 --> 11:01.230
and do not come back.

11:01.230 --> 11:02.070
Understood.

11:02.120 --> 11:02.830
Freeze!

11:40.910 --> 11:42.700
When did you discover my identity?

11:42.700 --> 11:43.990
I never did, actually.

11:44.750 --> 11:46.270
I tested everyone,

11:46.720 --> 11:49.380
and you were the only one
who gave yourself away.

11:49.670 --> 11:51.510
The caltrop fireball is way too important.

11:51.510 --> 11:53.040
If Feng An were discovered,

11:53.580 --> 11:57.510
his accomplices would have no choice
but to put their lives on the line.

12:00.510 --> 12:02.030
Actually, ever since

12:02.030 --> 12:03.310
I first saw you by Mao's side,

12:03.310 --> 12:04.710
something felt off to me.

12:05.000 --> 12:06.320
The woman who once had the courage

12:06.320 --> 12:08.000
to die alongside
Prince Changsha...

12:08.000 --> 12:10.440
If you drink it, you'll die too.

12:10.670 --> 12:12.130
Then I'll go down with him.

12:13.600 --> 12:15.720
How could she, after falling for someone,

12:15.720 --> 12:19.050
willingly copy another person
and live as her replacement?

12:20.150 --> 12:23.080
You were Eagle King's agent
from the very beginning.

12:24.320 --> 12:25.550
I don't think so.

12:26.440 --> 12:29.170
At first, she was probably
just an inactive pawn—

12:29.480 --> 12:33.200
disguised as a dancer,
gathering intelligence all over Jiankang.

12:33.200 --> 12:34.480
When Prince Changsha rebelled,

12:34.480 --> 12:35.830
she realized something had changed.

12:35.830 --> 12:37.360
To avoid being dragged into it,

12:37.360 --> 12:39.090
she fled the Lantai gathering.

12:39.320 --> 12:41.240
She never expected to run into you,

12:41.240 --> 12:44.900
and by a twist of fate, she ended up
in Prince Jing'an's Household.

12:45.750 --> 12:46.960
So you never really

12:46.960 --> 12:48.760
intended to save those dancers?

12:49.120 --> 12:50.360
You just wanted to create chaos

12:50.360 --> 12:51.490
so you could escape?

12:51.720 --> 12:53.320
Everyone has their own fate.

12:53.910 --> 12:56.790
As a spy, I can't afford to
worry about such things.

12:56.790 --> 12:58.600
You used Prince Jing'an's Household
as a stepping stone

12:58.600 --> 12:59.790
to get close to me,

13:00.120 --> 13:02.190
taking it one step at a time

13:02.210 --> 13:03.510
to see how far you could go.

13:03.510 --> 13:05.630
Precisely because you had no plan at all,

13:05.630 --> 13:07.270
you left no traces behind.

13:07.970 --> 13:08.640
You even

13:08.830 --> 13:11.750
deliberately arranged for Feng An
to come to my side,

13:11.750 --> 13:13.280
drawing my attention away.

13:13.440 --> 13:14.910
But you still found out.

13:16.040 --> 13:17.510
Since you had already caught Feng An,

13:17.510 --> 13:19.370
why were you still not at assured?

13:21.000 --> 13:22.840
Things have always been like this

13:22.840 --> 13:25.040
for lonely rulers throughout history.

13:27.150 --> 13:28.950
Do you have anything else to say?

13:30.840 --> 13:31.700
Your Highness.

13:32.960 --> 13:36.750
I have no complaints or regrets
in this life.

13:37.850 --> 13:40.610
I only wish Your Highness to take care

13:41.390 --> 13:42.850
and achieve your desires.

13:51.120 --> 13:52.520
By His Majesty's decree:

13:52.980 --> 13:55.360
3 days from now, on the auspicious day,
the imperial army—

13:55.360 --> 13:56.960
fully prepared and in high spirits—

13:56.960 --> 13:58.790
will set out on the Northern Expedition.

13:58.790 --> 14:01.250
All Northern Qin spies
within Jiankang City

14:01.910 --> 14:03.840
shall be sacrificed to the banner!

14:04.730 --> 14:05.860
Yes, Your Highness!

14:20.010 --> 14:21.670
The Northern Qin barbarians,

14:22.150 --> 14:24.840
with the nature of jackals and wolves,
have usurped the Central Plains

14:24.840 --> 14:27.370
and torn our land apart
for more than 20 years.

14:27.520 --> 14:29.230
They burned our ancestral temples,

14:29.230 --> 14:30.630
plundered our classics,

14:30.870 --> 14:33.370
trampled the nine-tiered imperial palaces
of the Capital,

14:33.370 --> 14:36.150
and defiled the clear skies
and fertile lands in Heluo.

14:36.150 --> 14:39.620
The gray-haired survivors still remember
the blood spilled before Zhuque Street,

14:39.620 --> 14:43.820
and young children still hear the cries
lingering on in the ancestral hall.

14:44.120 --> 14:45.510
Unless this grudge is avenged,

14:45.510 --> 14:47.770
how can we stand before Heaven and Earth?

14:47.840 --> 14:49.150
Now our iron-clad armies have endured
the autumn campaigns,

14:49.150 --> 14:50.270
our night watches have echoed
without rest,

14:50.270 --> 14:52.440
and the imperial forces
have fully gathered their strength.

14:52.440 --> 14:55.360
From the Observatory, we see
the purple aura gathering in the east.

14:55.360 --> 14:58.870
From the Yellow River, we hear
the thunderous roar shaking the north.

14:58.870 --> 15:00.850
How can we bear to watch
the barbarian dust obscure the sun?

15:00.850 --> 15:03.270
How dare we forget the heart-wrenching
anguish of our ancestors?

15:03.270 --> 15:05.790
Those who behead enemy soldiers
shall be rewarded with 1000 taels of gold;

15:05.790 --> 15:08.390
those who seize banners or break through
enemy lines shall be granted a fief of

15:08.390 --> 15:09.910
10000 households.
On the day this proclamation reaches you,

15:09.910 --> 15:11.870
we shall unfurl the dragon banners
upon Mount Yin,

15:11.870 --> 15:14.000
hang the heads of Qin spies at Hangu Pass,

15:14.000 --> 15:16.340
restore the radiance of sun and moon
over the ancient realm,

15:16.340 --> 15:18.150
and rebuild our mountains and rivers
upon the old borders.

15:17.940 --> 15:20.040
[Beifu]

15:18.840 --> 15:21.080
The 3 armies jointly swear
this blood oath:

15:21.080 --> 15:22.670
Until our realm is restored,

15:22.670 --> 15:24.980
our blades shall not return to
their sheaths.

15:24.980 --> 15:27.400
[Xiyue Restaurant]

15:31.270 --> 15:31.910
Lan!

15:32.230 --> 15:32.870
Lan!

15:33.720 --> 15:34.440
Chuan?

15:34.840 --> 15:35.480
Chuan!

15:39.960 --> 15:41.890
Young Lord Xiao found you after all.

15:41.890 --> 15:43.410
[Jing Lan's brother Jing Chuan]

15:42.050 --> 15:44.310
Young Lord Xiao left this letter for you.

15:48.100 --> 15:49.790
"I depart on a journey
from which I may not return.

15:49.790 --> 15:52.990
I hereby return Xiyue Restaurant
to its rightful owner."

16:10.840 --> 16:11.840
The Imperial Envoy came again?

16:11.840 --> 16:12.700
Your Highness.

16:13.240 --> 16:16.190
His Majesty has learned that
the Southern Ye Army

16:16.270 --> 16:17.290
has crossed the Jing River
and captured Luyang.

16:17.290 --> 16:18.160
The court and the public are in an uproar.

16:18.160 --> 16:20.490
His Majesty has granted Your Highness
the ceremonial tiger token

16:20.490 --> 16:24.300
and ordered Your Highness to immediately
dispatch troops to face the enemy.

16:24.300 --> 16:27.020
My dear nephew finally
couldn't hold back anymore.

16:27.020 --> 16:28.870
For 3 years he wouldn't give me
the tiger token,

16:28.870 --> 16:30.080
but now that Luyang has fallen,

16:30.080 --> 16:31.680
he's sent it over so quickly.

16:32.910 --> 16:34.320
Chan had already delivered

16:34.320 --> 16:36.080
the military strategy simulations

16:36.080 --> 16:37.670
Xiao Wuyi did for Li Mao in prison to me.

16:37.670 --> 16:38.960
Prince Qi is far too impatient.

16:38.960 --> 16:41.750
He actually just copied their idea

16:42.030 --> 16:43.270
and attacked

16:43.470 --> 16:46.070
our weakest western defense line

16:47.250 --> 16:48.840
without giving it any thought.

16:48.840 --> 16:52.030
How could a leisurely prince
who knows nothing but poetry and prose

16:52.030 --> 16:54.120
possibly understand military tactics?

16:54.120 --> 16:56.750
As long as the Beifu soldiers
continue to attack the western front,

16:56.750 --> 16:59.790
the cities behind it
won't be easy to capture.

17:00.910 --> 17:02.060
Do not underestimate our enemy.

17:02.060 --> 17:02.790
Understood.

17:03.200 --> 17:04.060
Your Highness.

17:04.880 --> 17:07.400
Last night we caught a small-time bandit

17:07.829 --> 17:10.960
who actually tried to raid the camp
and rescue Xiao Wuyi.

17:10.960 --> 17:11.680
Someone,

17:12.349 --> 17:13.109
bring him up!

17:18.640 --> 17:19.700
It's actually him.

17:20.650 --> 17:21.910
He's still alive, huh?

17:23.109 --> 17:23.920
Alright then.

17:24.240 --> 17:25.720
Take him to the torture chamber

17:25.720 --> 17:28.440
and have him reunite with
Xiao Wuyi's another guard.

17:28.440 --> 17:30.370
Aren't we sending him to Xiao Wuyi?

17:30.590 --> 17:31.440
These days,

17:31.550 --> 17:33.070
we've tried both carrots and sticks
on him,

17:33.070 --> 17:34.160
but he just wouldn't budge.

17:34.160 --> 17:35.960
He even managed to escape 3 times.

17:35.960 --> 17:37.640
If he were to give in that easily,

17:37.640 --> 17:40.270
I'd find it suspicious. Take him away.

17:42.310 --> 17:43.720
Will you talk or not?

17:44.400 --> 17:45.530
Will you talk or not?

17:45.830 --> 17:48.090
His Highness the Eagle King has arrived!

17:50.830 --> 17:53.030
What a loyal young lady.

17:53.510 --> 17:56.200
We caught an old friend of yours
last night.

18:01.720 --> 18:02.480
Qing Long?

18:04.190 --> 18:05.350
He followed us all the way here.

18:05.350 --> 18:07.880
He had been hiding outside the camp
for the past few days,

18:07.880 --> 18:10.790
trying everything to save Xiao Wuyi,
but failed.

18:12.100 --> 18:13.930
And he was caught last night.

18:18.110 --> 18:19.790
Since you survived,
you should try to remain that way!

18:19.790 --> 18:20.920
Why come here to die?

18:21.510 --> 18:23.350
There are no deserters in the Beifu Army.

18:23.350 --> 18:25.080
With you and His Highness here,

18:25.440 --> 18:27.720
if I hadn't come to save you
and had chosen to flee for my own life,

18:27.720 --> 18:29.850
what kind of friend would that make me?

18:30.960 --> 18:31.960
If you're scared,

18:32.200 --> 18:34.290
just hand over the chance to go to
Northern Qin with His Highness.

18:34.290 --> 18:34.770
Quiet.

18:35.110 --> 18:35.830
Me, scared?

18:36.070 --> 18:37.350
I'm just worried
that if I don't win the draw,

18:37.350 --> 18:38.680
you'll steal my chance

18:38.680 --> 18:39.940
to prove myself again.

18:51.240 --> 18:52.070
A bet is a bet.

18:52.350 --> 18:53.000
I won.

18:53.590 --> 18:55.190
His Highness and I will go to Northern Qin
as bait,

18:55.190 --> 18:57.050
and you'll lay in ambush outside.

18:57.440 --> 18:59.030
Honestly, there was never any need
for a draw.

18:59.030 --> 19:00.110
With a brain like yours,

19:00.110 --> 19:02.970
how could you possibly outmaneuver
the Eagle King?

19:14.270 --> 19:17.550
How many times do you plan to
pull that trick on him?

19:28.720 --> 19:30.450
I hope this isn't the last time.

19:39.550 --> 19:40.480
Go get some rest.

19:41.270 --> 19:44.270
We're hitting the road
first thing tomorrow morning.

20:11.060 --> 20:11.890
Rest assured, Your Highness.

20:11.890 --> 20:14.110
I'll try to stage a few more
rescue attempts before I get captured.

20:14.110 --> 20:16.310
That way, it will seem more convincing.

20:16.790 --> 20:18.590
Don't lose your life doing this.

20:18.880 --> 20:20.160
Even if I do, it doesn't matter.

20:20.160 --> 20:21.160
A suicide mission

20:21.230 --> 20:23.160
can't work without someone dying.

20:27.040 --> 20:29.170
Is that why you refused to tell Yan Yue?

20:32.770 --> 20:33.970
She's soft-hearted.

20:34.070 --> 20:36.750
And she'd definitely choose to be
the one waiting outside.

20:36.750 --> 20:37.890
A prison break is like a gamble—

20:37.890 --> 20:39.890
the slightest mistake means death.

20:40.030 --> 20:40.920
I'll do it.

20:51.160 --> 20:53.350
You two share such a deep bond of
affection and loyalty,

20:53.350 --> 20:55.350
which makes you ideal subjects
for interrogation.

20:55.350 --> 20:58.310
I've witnessed Miss Yan Yue's loyalty
with my own eyes.

20:58.310 --> 21:02.710
But since ancient times, it's been hard
to balance loyalty and righteousness.

21:03.350 --> 21:04.160
Young man.

21:04.640 --> 21:05.840
Do you want to know

21:07.040 --> 21:08.570
if she has feelings for you?

21:11.000 --> 21:12.070
I can help you.

21:16.000 --> 21:16.600
Qing Long!

21:25.020 --> 21:26.820
Torture them one after another.

21:27.160 --> 21:28.960
Since this lady refuses to talk,

21:29.350 --> 21:30.640
keep interrogating him.

21:30.640 --> 21:32.300
One of them is bound to give in.

21:33.330 --> 21:34.460
Yes, Your Highness.

22:26.920 --> 22:28.500
Take a look, Young Lord Xiao,

22:28.500 --> 22:30.790
These two were so affectionate
and loyal to each other,

22:30.790 --> 22:32.590
yet they only held out for 4 hours

22:33.190 --> 22:36.320
before drawing this defense map
of the Northern Border.

22:38.680 --> 22:39.350
You're truly a man

22:39.350 --> 22:41.080
without a shred of compassion.

22:41.350 --> 22:42.950
You're nothing but a stray dog,

22:42.950 --> 22:44.480
yet they've followed you
through thick and thin.

22:44.480 --> 22:46.130
Aren't you moved at all?

22:47.070 --> 22:49.550
Aren't their lives worth more than
Li Mao's?

22:51.050 --> 22:53.440
The soldiers of our Beifu Army
have always risked their lives

22:53.440 --> 22:55.100
to protect the common people.

22:56.480 --> 22:57.880
You want me to betray Ye

22:58.310 --> 23:00.270
and abandon the people of
the Northern Border

23:00.270 --> 23:01.680
just to save their lives?

23:01.960 --> 23:02.750
Mulian Yu,

23:03.510 --> 23:05.240
when did you become so foolish?

23:05.510 --> 23:07.550
Now that you've mentioned
the common people,

23:07.550 --> 23:09.110
this is perfect. Guards,

23:09.920 --> 23:11.580
bring the common people over!

23:13.480 --> 23:14.110
Move!

23:14.200 --> 23:15.130
Faster! Faster!

23:15.350 --> 23:16.270
Move! Faster!

23:16.550 --> 23:17.200
Move!

23:17.200 --> 23:18.440
Move! Get in!

23:18.550 --> 23:19.200
Hurry up!

23:19.680 --> 23:20.960
Move faster!

23:21.310 --> 23:22.640
Move! Faster!

23:22.640 --> 23:24.310
The weather's perfect today—

23:24.640 --> 23:26.440
an excellent chance for
a 100-pace archery contest.

23:26.440 --> 23:27.310
Back in Jiankang,

23:27.310 --> 23:28.270
I lost to you.

23:28.790 --> 23:30.590
Let's have another match today.

23:30.640 --> 23:31.880
If I lose again,

23:32.070 --> 23:34.000
I'll set Qing Long and Yan Yue free.

23:40.640 --> 23:42.040
Do you guys know who he is?

23:42.480 --> 23:44.240
He's none other than Crown Prince Wenxi,

23:44.240 --> 23:45.790
the one you've spent your entire lives
waiting for!

23:45.790 --> 23:49.160
Save us, Your Highness!

23:49.920 --> 23:50.780
Please save us!

23:52.750 --> 23:55.110
Over these years, the rumor
"when the Phoenix Heart Tokens appear,

23:55.110 --> 23:57.070
peace shall be restored in the world"
has spread far and wide—

23:57.070 --> 23:59.270
not only across Southern Ye,
but even in the Capital.

23:59.270 --> 24:00.640
Who among these refugees from Southern Ye

24:00.640 --> 24:03.790
does not long for you, Crown Prince Wenxi,
to reappear in this world

24:03.790 --> 24:06.050
and rescue them from their dire straits?

24:06.880 --> 24:08.400
Now that you've come here,

24:09.510 --> 24:10.640
I'm curious to see

24:11.000 --> 24:13.350
if you can really
turn a blind eye to them.

24:33.180 --> 24:33.830
Shoot!

24:43.590 --> 24:44.310
Stop!

24:55.680 --> 24:58.400
The defense map drawn by Xiao Wuyi

24:59.060 --> 25:01.350
is different from the one
drawn by Qing Long and Yan Yue.

25:01.350 --> 25:02.640
Which one is right?

25:03.240 --> 25:05.240
We'll know once we put it to the test.

25:19.830 --> 25:21.160
From 3 to 5 a.m. this morning,

25:21.160 --> 25:23.030
Eagle King dispatched 3 scouting units

25:23.030 --> 25:24.550
to launch feigned attacks on Qingxi,

25:24.550 --> 25:26.270
Yingchuan, and Sansha.

25:28.110 --> 25:29.040
What about Wuyi?

25:29.110 --> 25:30.640
Is there any news about him?

25:32.180 --> 25:32.900
Not yet.

25:33.590 --> 25:37.190
But the fact that Eagle King
feigned attacks on those 3 locations

25:37.240 --> 25:39.440
shows that he's starting to trust Wuyi.

25:39.720 --> 25:41.960
Wuyi's plan is halfway to success.

25:42.190 --> 25:43.240
Eagle King is cunning.

25:43.240 --> 25:44.640
We can't fully trust him.

25:45.240 --> 25:47.240
I must make sure he comes back alive.

25:50.000 --> 25:50.600
By the way,

25:51.200 --> 25:52.580
an old acquaintance returned last night.

25:52.580 --> 25:54.510
He said he had something very important
to give you,

25:54.510 --> 25:56.570
and that it could only be given to you.

25:56.680 --> 25:57.270
Who is it?

25:57.850 --> 25:58.680
Be careful.

26:03.960 --> 26:04.720
Cui Shao'an?

26:06.680 --> 26:07.680
How have you been?

26:07.680 --> 26:09.160
Thankfully, I've fulfilled the task
you entrusted to me.

26:09.160 --> 26:09.790
I found it.

26:10.920 --> 26:12.350
Just as you said in the letter,

26:12.350 --> 26:13.270
it's not ore,

26:13.470 --> 26:15.270
but a slurry-like substance.

26:21.020 --> 26:22.110
Get the caltrop fireball ready.

26:22.110 --> 26:23.290
We'll test it right now.

26:23.290 --> 26:24.720
You must be extra careful.

26:24.720 --> 26:27.270
The power of this thing goes far beyond
your imagination.

26:27.270 --> 26:28.440
No matter how dangerous it is,
we must try it.

26:28.440 --> 26:29.830
Ancient texts record
that the caltrop fireball

26:29.830 --> 26:30.960
burns with the force of
a collapsing mountain,

26:30.960 --> 26:32.620
its flames twisting like lightning,

26:32.620 --> 26:35.550
capable of determining victory
across vast fields.

26:35.590 --> 26:36.830
To win this battle,

26:37.390 --> 26:39.320
and to ensure Wuyi returns safely,

26:39.440 --> 26:42.240
no matter how dangerous it is,
we must give it a try.

26:43.440 --> 26:45.400
The three groups of scouts I dispatched,

26:45.400 --> 26:47.270
following the map you drew,

26:47.550 --> 26:49.280
were indeed completely wiped out.

26:49.280 --> 26:51.810
It seems this map is correct.

26:52.550 --> 26:54.810
Have Qing Long and Yan Yue been released?

26:55.000 --> 26:56.240
I always keep my word—

26:56.890 --> 26:58.350
as long as you cooperate with me.

26:58.350 --> 27:00.350
There are 2 subtle errors on this map

27:00.470 --> 27:01.730
that I left on purpose.

27:02.510 --> 27:04.240
If Your Highness wants to
cooperate with me,

27:04.240 --> 27:06.640
you must first agree to
one more condition.

27:09.210 --> 27:10.300
That's good.

27:10.400 --> 27:12.460
That's more like the Xiao Wuyi I know.

27:12.480 --> 27:14.350
Go ahead. What condition is it?

27:14.790 --> 27:15.850
I want the Capital.

27:19.830 --> 27:21.160
I'm Crown Prince Wenxi.

27:22.000 --> 27:25.660
I'm determined to lead the people of Ye
back to our former capital.

27:26.270 --> 27:28.160
Xiao Wuyi, oh, Xiao Wuyi.

27:28.830 --> 27:31.490
Your demand is a little too ambitious,
isn't it?

27:32.590 --> 27:33.720
At this point,

27:34.440 --> 27:37.300
is Your Highness really in any position
to bargain?

27:38.890 --> 27:41.480
The young emperor of Northern Qin
is wary of you—

27:41.480 --> 27:44.110
he's cut off your supplies,
sent a military inspector,

27:44.110 --> 27:45.110
and now seeks to use Li Mao's forces

27:45.110 --> 27:48.490
to wipe out your remaining 30,000
Black Eagle Army soldiers.

27:48.490 --> 27:51.210
Now that a blade's already pressed against
Your Highness's neck,

27:51.210 --> 27:52.740
do you really have a choice?

27:52.950 --> 27:55.670
I don't want a single soldier
from Your Highness.

27:55.670 --> 27:57.600
I only want the survivors of our Ye.

27:58.210 --> 27:59.680
If I was able to build one Beifu Army,

27:59.680 --> 28:01.280
then I can build a second one.

28:02.400 --> 28:05.160
When the time comes, you and I
will join forces to defeat Li Mao's army.

28:05.160 --> 28:06.400
You can then march south

28:06.400 --> 28:07.660
and capture Jiankang,

28:08.030 --> 28:09.560
and then advance westward.

28:16.790 --> 28:19.030
What, did I hit the nail on the head?

28:20.240 --> 28:21.570
Isn't the land of Xizhou

28:22.150 --> 28:24.010
what Your Highness desires most?

28:29.240 --> 28:30.100
Your Highness!

28:36.000 --> 28:38.200
Are you really going to
hand the Capital over to Xiao Wuyi?

28:38.200 --> 28:39.590
That's treason.

28:42.510 --> 28:44.750
So that was a lie, Your Highness?

28:45.350 --> 28:46.510
Once you get

28:46.510 --> 28:48.310
the complete Northern Border
defense map from him

28:48.310 --> 28:49.680
and crush Li Mao's army,

28:49.680 --> 28:50.440
then

28:51.200 --> 28:52.660
we can get rid of Xiao Wuyi.

28:53.350 --> 28:54.590
But that Xiao Wuyi

28:54.590 --> 28:55.640
is far too clever.

28:56.620 --> 28:58.220
He saw right through the fact

28:58.360 --> 29:00.800
that what I desire most is Xizhou.

29:01.920 --> 29:03.640
Could it be that he has set
some kind of trap

29:03.640 --> 29:05.640
and is waiting for me to fall into it?

29:07.370 --> 29:10.300
If Your Highness remains
concerned about Xiao Wuyi,

29:10.800 --> 29:13.730
why not force him into a corner
where he has no way out?

29:13.920 --> 29:16.480
Your Highness, are you still unwell today?

29:17.630 --> 29:20.090
I've recovered.
I shall receive the decree.

29:24.510 --> 29:26.240
Southern Ye harbors the ambitions
of a wild beast,

29:26.240 --> 29:27.640
coveting our territory.

29:27.960 --> 29:29.960
They're truly a great threat
to our nation.

29:29.960 --> 29:31.000
Upon hearing the news,

29:31.000 --> 29:33.160
I wished I could immediately don my armor
and take the battlefield myself,

29:33.160 --> 29:34.960
fighting the enemy to the death.

29:35.160 --> 29:36.570
I hereby order you
to lead the counterattack,

29:36.570 --> 29:37.570
hold the line at Luyang,

29:37.570 --> 29:38.900
reclaim our lost lands,

29:39.160 --> 29:41.200
and avenge this national humiliation.

29:41.200 --> 29:42.920
As for Xiao Wuyi,
use him if he proves capable.

29:42.920 --> 29:44.050
If not, execute him.

29:44.790 --> 29:47.810
If you fear that Xiao Wuyi
might carry out a suicide mission,

29:47.810 --> 29:52.490
I have a way to help you test
Xiao Wuyi's true intentions.

30:12.720 --> 30:13.350
Eat up.

30:14.180 --> 30:16.780
Your brother has arrived
outside Luyang City.

30:16.810 --> 30:18.210
He can bring you home now.

30:33.830 --> 30:37.230
This is the sound of our Beifu Army's
war drums as they charge.

30:41.910 --> 30:45.510
Our young emperor's army
has already crossed the Qin Mountains.

30:46.070 --> 30:48.550
Right now, with the Beifu Army
ahead of me

30:49.200 --> 30:51.320
and our young emperor's army behind me,

30:51.320 --> 30:54.160
two sharp blades
are pressed against my head.

30:54.800 --> 30:57.860
Young Lord Xiao, you're the only one
who can save me now.

30:59.370 --> 31:00.300
Young Lord Xiao.

31:00.920 --> 31:02.200
Can you show me

31:02.480 --> 31:03.440
and the world

31:03.870 --> 31:04.940
this reason?

31:08.200 --> 31:09.530
What do you want me to do?

31:09.790 --> 31:11.250
I remember a few years ago,

31:11.260 --> 31:12.860
at Lingfeng Fort in Guazhou,

31:12.920 --> 31:14.780
Li Lejun murdered Princess Yunzhao

31:14.780 --> 31:15.950
and returned to Jiankang.

31:15.950 --> 31:18.820
You and Xie Jiayu teamed up
to uncover the real culprit.

31:18.820 --> 31:21.350
You originally wanted to
kill that murderer,

31:21.430 --> 31:22.990
but Li Lejun clung to life

31:23.070 --> 31:24.590
and voluntarily defected to me.

31:24.590 --> 31:26.830
Back then, Xie Jiayu once said:

31:27.480 --> 31:28.510
"If one day

31:28.850 --> 31:30.260
I see Li Lejun again..."

31:30.290 --> 31:31.950
"I'll surely take your life."

31:35.050 --> 31:37.200
Your Northern Qin spies
truly live up to their reputation.

31:37.200 --> 31:39.060
They even overheard every word of

31:39.250 --> 31:41.030
my private conversation with Li Mao.

31:41.030 --> 31:42.590
Then may I ask, Young Lord Xiao,

31:42.590 --> 31:45.070
does that statement still stand?

31:53.240 --> 31:54.170
Young Lord Xiao.

31:55.200 --> 31:56.310
Today, I will

31:56.720 --> 31:59.050
give you a chance to fulfill your promise.

32:05.240 --> 32:06.900
The Northern Qin barbarians,

32:07.030 --> 32:08.830
with the nature of jackals and wolves,

32:08.830 --> 32:10.480
have usurped the Central Plains

32:10.480 --> 32:13.010
and torn our land apart
for more than 20 years.

32:13.510 --> 32:16.310
They trampled the nine-tiered
imperial palaces of the Capital,

32:16.310 --> 32:19.370
and defiled the clear skies
and fertile lands in Heluo.

32:19.440 --> 32:21.590
Now our iron-clad armies have endured
the autumn campaigns,

32:21.590 --> 32:23.310
our night watches have echoed
without rest,

32:23.310 --> 32:25.750
and the imperial forces
have fully gathered their strength.

32:25.750 --> 32:30.640
Those who seize banners or break through
enemy lines shall be granted 10000 households!

32:30.640 --> 32:33.240
Your Highness, they're not responding.
What should we do?

32:33.240 --> 32:34.570
Keep challenging them.

32:34.760 --> 32:36.210
Keep challenging them!

32:43.550 --> 32:46.210
Your Highness, someone has come out
over there.

32:51.550 --> 32:52.200
Lejun!

32:56.850 --> 32:58.830
Your brother is right across from us.

32:58.830 --> 33:00.160
He's here to pick you up.

33:02.750 --> 33:03.310
Go on.

33:05.790 --> 33:06.720
Mulian Yu.

33:08.160 --> 33:10.290
I don't regret coming to Northern Qin,

33:10.350 --> 33:11.950
nor do I regret marrying you.

33:13.350 --> 33:16.310
From the moment I stepped onto
the land of Northern Qin,

33:16.310 --> 33:19.400
I knew it would end like this.

33:21.590 --> 33:22.720
But in the next life,

33:25.950 --> 33:27.550
let's not cross paths again.

33:32.470 --> 33:33.270
Prince Qi!

33:34.590 --> 33:36.030
See clearly who I am!

33:36.680 --> 33:37.610
Let my sister go!

33:38.200 --> 33:41.240
If you're willing to trade Luyang City
for your sister's life,

33:41.240 --> 33:42.970
I'll release her immediately!

33:45.750 --> 33:46.680
Young Lord Xiao.

33:47.880 --> 33:49.750
The grudge of ruining your reputation
and taking your power,

33:49.750 --> 33:52.880
and the hatred of wiping out your clan
and taking your wife—

33:52.880 --> 33:55.080
the time has come to settle these debts.

34:13.880 --> 34:14.800
Xiao Wuyi.

34:15.570 --> 34:16.670
You traitor!

34:18.230 --> 34:19.360
Kill me if you want.

34:20.080 --> 34:23.000
I, Li Lejun, will never back down!

34:45.440 --> 34:46.159
Wuyi!

34:46.719 --> 34:47.550
No!

34:50.510 --> 34:51.150
Wait.

34:56.550 --> 34:59.630
Give Li Mao the chance to fire 3 arrows.

35:00.710 --> 35:01.880
I'd like to see

35:02.680 --> 35:05.340
if he's willing to sacrifice
his sister's life.

35:07.840 --> 35:09.150
Soldiers of Beifu!

35:10.190 --> 35:11.990
Xiao Wuyi has committed treason

35:12.400 --> 35:14.260
and surrendered to Northern Qin!

35:14.280 --> 35:16.190
He's no longer your commander!

35:16.780 --> 35:17.900
He's a traitor!

35:30.840 --> 35:31.670
Li Lejun?

35:41.470 --> 35:43.990
Young Lord Xiao, I hope you've been well.

35:45.050 --> 35:47.980
Weren't you put under house arrest
by the Eagle King?

35:49.340 --> 35:51.280
I've already taken a deadly poison.

35:51.280 --> 35:52.440
My time is almost up.

35:53.230 --> 35:54.710
What's the point of keeping me locked up?

35:54.710 --> 35:55.510
What?

36:01.110 --> 36:02.000
Xiao Wuyi.

36:03.070 --> 36:06.070
I came to ask you for a favor.

36:07.510 --> 36:09.800
Tomorrow, when the 2 armies
face off on the battlefield,

36:09.800 --> 36:10.730
could you please

36:11.030 --> 36:14.090
not let me die at the hands
of the Northern Qin soldiers?

36:14.840 --> 36:15.710
I hope

36:16.300 --> 36:17.740
you can kill me yourself.

36:21.190 --> 36:21.840
Reason?

36:22.440 --> 36:24.230
I owe Jiayu a life anyway.

36:25.280 --> 36:26.340
If you take my life,

36:27.880 --> 36:28.740
I can accept it.

36:38.590 --> 36:40.520
Your Highness! Your Highness, no!

36:52.800 --> 36:53.660
Could it be that

36:53.790 --> 36:56.320
Eagle King is just testing Wuyi
with all this?

36:56.420 --> 36:59.370
If Wuyi doesn't shoot Li Lejun
in front of the 2 armies,

36:59.370 --> 37:01.030
he'll be completely exposed,

37:01.440 --> 37:04.440
and the entire plan will fall apart
at the last moment.

37:05.000 --> 37:06.760
Soldiers of Ye!

37:07.920 --> 37:10.360
My brother has told me since I was young

37:10.710 --> 37:12.170
that the elite troops of Ye

37:12.370 --> 37:15.890
must fight for the land and people of Ye!

37:23.320 --> 37:25.110
I've already taken poison.

37:25.760 --> 37:27.760
Death is only a matter of time for me.

37:27.900 --> 37:29.740
But I'm Princess Pingning of Ye.

37:30.380 --> 37:33.340
My father, mother,
my brothers and sisters—

37:33.370 --> 37:36.150
so many of them were killed by
the people of Northern Qin.

37:36.150 --> 37:37.010
No matter what,

37:37.480 --> 37:38.550
I, Li Lejun,

37:39.510 --> 37:41.510
cannot die at their hands.

37:42.960 --> 37:43.760
This

37:45.400 --> 37:47.150
isn't the whole truth, is it?

37:52.280 --> 37:53.080
You're right.

37:55.550 --> 37:57.030
There's a third reason.

38:07.030 --> 38:07.880
Lejun!

38:09.360 --> 38:10.360
Lejun!

38:15.230 --> 38:16.550
Today,

38:17.840 --> 38:19.880
as I give my life for Ye,

38:21.040 --> 38:23.350
I die a worthy death.

38:25.800 --> 38:27.330
Soldiers of the Beifu Army!

38:28.000 --> 38:29.490
Li Mao killed my parents

38:30.080 --> 38:31.170
and took my wife.

38:31.400 --> 38:33.130
My hatred for him is boundless!

38:34.000 --> 38:36.400
The Eagle King has promised me
the Capital.

38:36.440 --> 38:37.640
If you surrender now,

38:38.230 --> 38:39.880
once we reclaim our homeland,

38:39.880 --> 38:41.810
you'll be granted rank and honors.

38:42.190 --> 38:44.250
As for those who refuse to surrender,

38:44.790 --> 38:46.920
when we meet again on the battlefield,

38:47.760 --> 38:49.350
expect no mercy.

38:51.110 --> 38:52.510
Your Highness Prince Qi!

38:52.960 --> 38:55.760
Your sister has sacrificed for you
her whole life!

38:56.670 --> 38:58.730
Yet you aren't willing to trade a city

38:59.070 --> 39:00.000
for her life?

39:04.000 --> 39:05.800
Your Highness has been hiding

39:05.800 --> 39:08.460
the Regent of Southern Ye's sister
all these years.

39:08.460 --> 39:12.540
How do you want to show His Majesty
your loyalty?

39:15.670 --> 39:16.600
Young Lord Xiao.

39:40.070 --> 39:41.280
Xiao Wuyi!

39:41.630 --> 39:42.490
Your Highness!

40:10.830 --> 40:14.230
If my brother is to become a true emperor,

40:15.590 --> 40:17.920
he must free himself from your influence—

40:19.030 --> 40:20.840
not only from your command
over the Beifu Army,

40:20.840 --> 40:23.370
but also from the hold you have
over his heart.

40:24.800 --> 40:25.920
I once thought

40:27.070 --> 40:28.670
you merely viewed my brother

40:28.880 --> 40:31.000
as a stepping stone to seize power.

40:31.230 --> 40:32.430
But now it seems

40:32.450 --> 40:35.980
you're even more ruthless toward yourself
than toward others,

40:36.710 --> 40:40.170
and you care even less about your status
as Crown Prince Wenxi.

40:40.710 --> 40:42.710
A person like you has no weaknesses.

40:43.990 --> 40:47.050
The line between god and demon
lies in a single thought.

40:47.230 --> 40:48.360
Yet if one day

40:49.960 --> 40:51.550
your paths diverge,

40:51.980 --> 40:54.420
what will become of my brother?

40:56.400 --> 40:58.060
If you truly have faith in him,

40:59.340 --> 41:00.660
then please allow him

41:01.840 --> 41:04.960
to stand before you as a true rival.
